sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Staff
    participant Sistem
    participant Basis Data

    Staff->>Sistem: Minta laporan
    Sistem->>Sistem: Verifikasi akun

    alt valid
        Sistem->>Basis Data: Ambil data tagihan
        Basis Data-->>Sistem: Data
        Sistem-->>Staff: Laporan
    else tidak valid
        Sistem-->>Staff: Kesalahan
    end